---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
import { SUPPORT_EMAIL, LEGAL_ENTITY } from "../config";
---
<LegalLayout lang="en" path="/terms" title="Terms of Service">
  <p>Last updated: <strong>June 22, 2026</strong>.</p>
  <p>
    These Terms govern your use of the <strong>Tattoo Inkprep</strong> app and this
    website, provided by <strong>{LEGAL_ENTITY}</strong> (Spain, EU). By using Inkprep you
    agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the service.
  </p>

  <h2>1. The service</h2>
  <p>
    Inkprep is a professional <strong>support tool</strong> for color tattoo artists. You
    upload a clean digital design and Inkprep suggests tattoo inks that match its colors,
    optionally adjusted to a client's skin tone.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Not advice, no guarantee of result</h2>
  <p>
    Inkprep provides <strong>color reference suggestions only</strong>. It is not medical
    advice and does not guarantee any specific tattoo outcome. The final result on skin
    depends on the ink, the technique, the client's skin and the lighting. As a
    professional, you remain solely responsible for the inks you use and the work you
    perform.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Limitation of liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the maximum extent permitted by law, {LEGAL_ENTITY} is not liable for any outcome
    of a tattoo, for decisions made based on the app's suggestions, or for indirect or
    consequential damages arising from use of the service. The recommendations are a guide,
    and professional judgment always prevails.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Your designs and intellectual property</h2>
  <p>
    The designs you upload remain <strong>yours</strong>. You grant us only a limited
    license to process and store them as needed to provide the service to you (e.g. to
    analyze colors and save your projects). You confirm you have the right to use any
    design you upload.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Acceptable use</h2>
  <p>
    You agree not to misuse the service, attempt to disrupt it, or upload content you have
    no right to use. We may suspend or terminate accounts that breach these Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Subscriptions</h2>
  <p>
    Inkprep is offered as a subscription through the app stores. Subscriptions
    <strong>renew automatically</strong> unless cancelled. You can manage or cancel your
    subscription at any time from your App Store account settings. Refunds are handled by
    Apple (or Google) under their applicable policies. Pricing and any trial are shown in
    the store at the moment of purchase.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Changes &amp; termination</h2>
  <p>
    We may update the service or these Terms; continued use means you accept the updated
    Terms. You may stop using the service and delete your account at any time.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about these Terms: <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
